caption: #contest Jack and Jack I got you on my mind, why should I get those tickets? The first reason is I don't have money to buy them and I adore them, I been there since day 1 the second reason, and the most important,  they are my life savers, maybe I wasn't bad at all but every song descrives my feelings, when I'm happy Paradise is the right song to listen to, when I'm sad distance or cold hearted, Wild Life makes me jump while I brush my teeth and the new ones? Calibraska? Don't get me started ?? even if I don't get those tickets so I can come see you in Barcelona thanks for being my heroes
